item.description:
create_session #
⚠️ Subject to change.
The instructor creates a new session.
{
// Request
&quot;request&quot;: &quot;create_session&quot;,
&quot;content&quot;: &quot;&quot;,
}
{
// Respond
&quot;content&quot;: &lt;int&gt;,
}
status_code: On success, 200. content: On success, server generated session ID. advance_stage #
⚠️ Subject to change.
The instructor advances the simulation to the next stage for all users. For example, from Welcome to Discussion #1.
{
// Request
&quot;request&quot;: &quot;advance_stage&quot;,
&quot;content&quot;: &lt;int&gt;,
}
content: -1, advance to next stage.

submit_poll #
⚠️ Subject to change.
The team submits their team decision poll.
{
// Continue from credentials
&quot;request&quot;: &quot;submit_poll&quot;,
&quot;content&quot;: {
&quot;poll_no&quot;: &lt;int&gt;,
&quot;poll_response&quot;: [xxx, xxx, xxx],
},
}
poll_no: 1 if 1st poll, 2 if 2nd poll. poll_response: An arrary. 0th item is response to 1st question.
